com.google.cloud.firestore.spi.v1beta1

Class GrpcFirestoreRpc

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.firestore.spi.v1beta1.GrpcFirestoreRpc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FirestoreRpc, ServiceRpc, AutoCloseable

    public class GrpcFirestoreRpc
extends Object
implements FirestoreRpc
    GRPC client implementation of the Firestore RPC methods. Exposes FirestoreOptions on top of the GRPC-based Firestore GAPIC client.
